rt of his youth in Normandy; and William claimed to have been nominated by Edward as his successor. Edward was canonized in the 12th century, and came to be venerated throughout Europe as a model of a Christian king."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Otwelus De Insula was born about 1129, in Gosforth, Northumberland, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son."},"et":{"Abt 1129–":"umbes 1129–Surnud","1160–Male":"1160–Surnud","1129–Male":"1129–Surnud","1129":"1129","1160":"1160","Abt 1129":"umbes 1129","Of, Gosforth, Northumberland, England":"Gosforth, Northumberland, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1129–":"noin 1129–Kuollut","1160–Male":"1160–Kuollut","1129–Male":"1129–Kuollut","1129":"1129","1160":"1160","Abt 1129":"noin 1129","Of, Gosforth, Northumberland, England":"Gosforth, Northumberland, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1129–":"environ 1129–Décédé","1160–Male":"1160–Décédé","1129–Male":"1129–Décédé","1129":"1129","1160":"1160","Abt 1129":"environ 1129","Of, Gosforth, Northumberland, England":"Gosforth, Northumberland, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Otwelus De Insula est né environ 1129, à Gosforth, Northumberland, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"Abt 1129–":"um 1129–Verstorben","1160–Male":"1160–Verstorben","1129–Male":"1129–Verstorben","1129":"1129","1160":"1160","Abt 1129":"um 1129","Of, Gosforth, Northumberland, England":"Gosforth, Northumberland, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Otwelus De Insula wurde um 1129 in Gosforth, Northumberland, England, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"Abt 1129–":"about 1129–Desede","1160–Male":"1160–Desede","1129–Male":"1129–Desede","1129":"1129","1160":"1160","Abt 1129":"about 1129","Of, Gosforth, Northumberland, England":"Gosforth, Northumberland, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"Abt 1129–":"1129 körül–elhunyt","1160–Male":"1160–elhunyt","1129–Male":"1129–elhunyt","1129":"1129","1160":"1160","Abt 1129":"1129 körül","Of, Gosforth, Northumberland